{"tid":1173301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"32歲女子山景邨墮樓重傷","createTime":"2019-05-27T04:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T12:36:31.000Z","uid":3090,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"17821d82218f3f61e1fb0109e41c119025c7816c","tid":1173301,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95g87fU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95g87fU.png&h=4106ea1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方封鎖現場調查。張家豪攝<br />\n<br />\n屯門山景邨景富樓，今早10時許，一名32歲女子懷疑從大廈高處墮下，重傷倒地，救護員接報到場將她送屯門醫院搶救，警方封鎖現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWF8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=794864f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"956fd1c8d319d0db83eeb1bb6f9629c10368a6d9","tid":1173301,"uid":69886,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"屯門垃圾地方係咁上下"},{"pid":"fe0e95ba2024689fb9eec293cf01d448383ce408","tid":1173301,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:21:41.000Z","msg":"福氣嚟架"},{"pid":"fbc25802fb77f478a8d11dc3dc2e7a0391628674","tid":1173301,"uid":253559,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"今天星期一到現在呢刻，已經有3位人士跳樓自殺⋯⋯"},{"pid":"0c130c3578412cb439ef8e0f17df356010139e28","tid":1173301,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:24:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cc17e66e80c4ee16ec2335d2cb94973953a0dec","tid":1173301,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c130c3578412cb439ef8e0f17df356010139e28","tid":1173301,"uid":52595,"lik